        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I hope you don't mind, but since the improvements for me were significant, I've implemented the cache part of this PR into a [plugin](https://github.com/lewis6991/impatient.nvim).\r\n\r\nIn addition to the cache, it:\r\n- Invalidates the cache using the module file's modified time. This appears to work well enough.\r\n- Stores the cache in `$XDG_CACHE_HOME`\r\n- Handles `mpack` for installs that don't have it.\r\n- Adds the `rtp` trick/hack to make uncached requires a little quicker.\r\n- Adds some simple commands to manage the cache.\r\n- Other bits of polish.\r\n\r\nObviously once we merge something into core the plugin will be obsolete, but in the meantime this should work well enough for most people.",
